{"tid":2121737,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"［大恩大德］慈雲山中心獲領展免租！！","createTime":"2020-07-23T13:38:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-23T16:51:25.000Z","uid":34571,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ca6600dd86616fbdccbc03739817a999109a9ff2","tid":2121737,"uid":34571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T13:38:37.000Z","msg":"兩日<br />\n<br />\n受第三波疫情影響，本港商場「減租潮」持續。領展行政總裁王國龍今天(22日)於股東周年大會上表示，旗下商場慈雲山中心，因應疫情關閉兩天，已免去受影響商戶兩天租金及管理費。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n王國龍又透露，疫情下公司受到不同程度的影響。旗下物業組合中有6成與超市、街市及食肆相關，其中超市及街市生意反而上升。另外續租率下跌亦見增加，公司將致力維持穩定出租率。<br />\n<br />\n另外，有報道指，繼2月至4月將租金減半後。九龍倉置業旗下海港城，決定進一步向商戶提供租金優惠，包括獲得5月的40%減租折扣。前提是商戶最少續租18個月，並付清6月30日前拖欠的租金及費用等條款，而商戶須於7月24日作出決定。"},{"pid":"9a12b05052bfcb8778267b92dbfb58ad267e7f6f","tid":2121737,"uid":155815,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T13:39:16.000Z","msg":"兩日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb59445c2e15f1d9a76ce44010ed7c4826592a8b","tid":2121737,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T13:40:37.000Z","msg":"豪畀狗都多過佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"625690e43c4e4ef3548d9fcfb6c0a4057aedffd3","tid":2121737,"uid":72173,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T13:42:10.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">兩天租金及管理費</span>"},{"pid":"9cb7e050789a03a76ad3b6f07595bf849c03c50f","tid":2121737,"uid":77968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T13:52:02.000Z","msg":"兩日<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n李嘉欣召喚"},{"pid":"9d41823572c958b88de488ee661849d073e7da18","tid":2121737,"uid":34571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T16:06:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"325c0b9fe65a25735a1771902a0f141a4aed07cc","tid":2121737,"uid":126590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-